2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper deals with wireless sensor networks, which are a subset of networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper may involve the use of algorithms and data structures to implement the proposed security architecture. 
4. cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper may involve the development of software for implementing the proposed security architecture.
